{"tid":1776840,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"如何處理藍屍","createTime":"2019-12-09T20:58:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-09T21:03:46.000Z","uid":279357,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"5cba6df6fbdc18d2006d1fee97ce1b696b41c75a","tid":1776840,"uid":279357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T20:58:28.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">每次活動都有班藍屍出呢<br />\n成群結隊人多勢眾甘出動<br />\n但總有落單既時候到時候<br />\n大家可以關愛下親切問候<br />\n呢種人一落單實怕到要死<br />\n嘈係無用既要威嚇等佢怕<br />\n下次班藍屍重邊敢再出呢<br />\n要用黑警亂拉人威嚇手法<br />\n對抗藍屍要知勇恨殺無赦<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"873b5cf258197b6bdb9da315dd59940534294653","tid":1776840,"uid":285514,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T21:03:46.000Z","msg":"一樣字數好似好犀利咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}